## Packages Overview

| Package | NPM name | Source | Output | Role |
|---------|----------|--------|--------|------|
| `packages/tokens` | `@neurex/tokens` | `src/` | `dist/` (+ generated CSS) | Design token source of truth, resolver, CSS/DTCG generators |
| `packages/ui` | `@neurex/ui` | `src/` | `dist/` | Reference React components (not what CLI ships to users) |
| `packages/registry` | `@neurex/registry` | `src/` + `templates/` | `dist/` + bundled templates | Install metadata + copyable templates for CLI |
| `packages/cli` | `neurex` | `src/` | `dist/` | CLI binary; reads registry, installs into consumer projects |

