## `packages/ui`

Reference implementations organized in three composition layers. Each item is a
**PascalCase folder** with:

- `ComponentName.tsx`
- `ComponentName.types.ts`
- `ComponentName.variants.ts`

```
packages/ui/
├── src/
│   ├── index.ts              # Public API — 32 primitives exported today
│   ├── utils/                # Shared UI utilities
│   └── components/
│       ├── primitives/       # 32 bundled primitives
│       ├── blocks/           # Pilot: FormField, Sidebar
│       └── templates/        # Pilot: DashboardShell
├── vitest.config.ts          # Vitest project config (jsdom)
└── test/
    ├── public-api.test.ts
    └── components/<Name>/    # Variant + render tests (primitives only)
```

**Primitives:** Accordion, Alert, AlertDialog, Avatar, Badge, Button, Card, Checkbox, Collapsible, Dialog, Drawer, Field, Fieldset, Form, Input, Menu, Meter, NumberField, Popover, Progress, RadioGroup, ScrollArea, Select, Separator, Slider, Switch, Tabs, Textarea, Toast, Toggle, ToggleGroup, Tooltip.

**Pilot blocks/templates:** FormField, Sidebar, DashboardShell — registry + CLI installable; sandbox QA in progress. See [UI_COMPOSITION.md](../../docs/UI_COMPOSITION.md).

Base UI (`@base-ui/react`) is internal; preserve accessibility when editing.

